# Healthcare AI System - Implementation Plan

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Frontend["Frontend (Next.js + Material UI)"]
        UI[Dashboard UI]
        PL[Patient List]
        DS[Discharge Summary Input]
        DR[Diagnosis Results]
        TP[Treatment Plans]
    end

    subgraph Backend["Backend (Django REST)"]
        API[REST API Layer]
        PM[Patient Manager]
        RAG[RAG Pipeline]
        GR[GraphRAG Engine]
        BE[BERT Engine]
        LLM[LLM Engine]
    end

    subgraph Models["AI Models"]
        BB[BioBERT / PubMedBERT]
        DS1[DeepSeek R1]
        M42[Med42]
        PML[PMC LLaMA]
    end

    subgraph Database["MySQL Database"]
        PT[Patients Table]
        DT[Diagnoses Table]
        TT[Treatments Table]
        KG[Knowledge Graph Store]
    end

    UI --> API
    API --> PM --> PT
    API --> RAG
    RAG --> GR --> KG
    RAG --> BE --> BB
    RAG --> LLM --> DS1
    LLM --> M42
    LLM --> PML
    GR --> BE
    BE --> LLM
    LLM --> DT
    LLM --> TT
```

## Pipeline Flow

```
Discharge Summary в†’ BioBERT NER в†’ Entity Extraction в†’ GraphRAG Knowledge Graph
                                                            в†“
                                                    Context Retrieval
                                                            в†“
                                            LLM Ensemble (DeepSeek + Med42 + PMC LLaMA)
                                                            в†“
                                                    Diagnosis + Treatment Plan
```

## Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | Next.js 14, React, Material UI 5 |
| Backend | Django 5, Django REST Framework |
| Database | MySQL 8 |
| BERT Models | BioBERT, PubMedBERT |
| LLMs | DeepSeek R1, Med42, PMC LLaMA |
| RAG | Custom GraphRAG implementation |
| Knowledge Graph | NetworkX + Medical Ontologies |

