## Implementation Phases

### Phase 1: Backend Setup
- Django project configuration
- MySQL database models
- 30 patient discharge summaries
- REST API endpoints

### Phase 2: AI Pipeline
- BioBERT/PubMedBERT entity extraction
- GraphRAG knowledge graph construction
- LLM integration layer (DeepSeek R1, Med42, PMC LLaMA)
- RAG pipeline orchestration

### Phase 3: Frontend
- Next.js project setup
- Material UI theme and components
- Dashboard, Patient List, Diagnosis views
- API integration

### Phase 4: Integration & Demo
- End-to-end pipeline testing
- Performance optimization
- Documentation
